---
title: Carb Smart Turkey Cheese-Stuffed Meatballs  with Cauliflower Mash
description: Juicy meatballs get stuffed with gooey mozzarella cheese in this savoury dinner! Cauliflower mash and roasted carrots are comforting sides for these cheese-filled bites of heaven.

